caption.p: The content of glycerol released into the medium. Each value is the mean Â± SD of three determinations and from three independent assays. Different letters ( a,b,c,d) indicate a significant difference ( p < 0.05) between the changes of the medium for same sample; Different numbers ( 1,2,3,4) indicate a significant difference ( p < 0.05) between the same change of the medium in the different samples.
